"587","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"588","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"589","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum"
"590","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"591","semi-monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"592","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"593","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"594","investments under the minimum."
